01:44:56.800 --> 01:45:01.298
lungs and causing your chest to seize just from
breathing the air in. I need both you and her to

01:45:01.298 --> 01:45:13.859
make a... The area is now heavily obscured, so now
there is a heavy smoke all in this area right now.

01:45:13.859 --> 01:45:16.278
LAURA: Does his head peek up above that?

01:45:16.278 --> 01:45:17.863
MATT: Yes, it does.

01:45:17.863 --> 01:45:19.607
LAURA: He's so tall.

01:45:19.607 --> 01:45:24.515
MATT: You don't do anything yet.

