TRAVIS: Nothing yet?

01:45:26.128 --> 01:45:27.542
MATT: You don't do anything yet.

01:45:27.542 --> 01:45:28.713
TRAVIS: On my turn.

01:45:28.713 --> 01:45:29.792
MATT: On your turn, you'll do it.

01:45:29.792 --> 01:45:31.642
SAM: Does that affect the fire elemental, too?

01:45:31.642 --> 01:45:32.821
MATT: It may.

01:45:32.821 --> 01:45:34.775
LAURA: You don't know.

01:45:34.775 --> 01:45:41.455
SAM: I don't. Sam Five has his theories, though.

