01:46:45.782 --> 01:46:47.285
SAM: Oh, that's great.

01:46:47.285 --> 01:46:58.639
MATT: That ends Raishan's turn. At the end of
Raishan's turn, Thordak is going to do another

01:46:58.639 --> 01:47:00.339
wing attack.

01:47:00.339 --> 01:47:05.395
LIAM: Man, Groggy. 17 displacer beasts just
appear.

01:47:05.395 --> 01:47:09.782
LAURA: Like, why would he add wyverns? For his own
sake!

01:47:09.782 --> 01:47:17.105
MATT: He's going to do another wing attack, at the
cost of two of its actions. Picking up the wind

01:47:17.105 --> 01:47:25.535
around it once more, I need Grog... Kima's just
out of the range, thankfully. Grog, I need you to

01:47:25.535 --> 01:47:27.471
make a dexterity saving throw.

01:47:27.471 --> 01:47:29.267
TRAVIS: I have advantage because of--

01:47:29.267 --> 01:47:30.536
MATT: You do.

01:47:30.536 --> 01:47:32.880
LAURA: Would the wings disperse the gas on the
ground?

01:47:32.880 --> 01:47:34.401
MATT: Nope! But it does push it.

01:47:34.401 --> 01:47:36.042
LAURA: Damn it.

01:47:36.042 --> 01:47:37.326
MARISHA: Oh, boy.

01:47:37.326 --> 01:47:39.376
TRAVIS: 17.

01:47:39.376 --> 01:47:41.773
MATT: 17, nope. You take--

01:47:41.773 --> 01:47:43.130
LAURA: Oh, no!

01:47:43.130 --> 01:47:46.801
MATT: 16 points of bludgeoning damage, reduced to
eight.

01:47:46.801 --> 01:47:47.973
TRAVIS: Okay.

01:47:47.973 --> 01:47:53.864
MATT: And you take eight points of fire damage,
reduced to four, from the impact, and you are

01:47:53.864 --> 01:48:04.625
