01:48:42.362 --> 01:48:46.968
MATT: 19, you succeed. You manage to just hold
your breath, and the poison doesn't makes its way

01:48:46.968 --> 01:48:48.735
and fit into your lungs.

01:48:48.735 --> 01:48:51.738
MARISHA: So, I still have this asshole in front of
me, right?

01:48:51.738 --> 01:48:53.608
MATT: Yes, you do.

01:48:53.608 --> 01:48:55.125
MARISHA: But he's been pushed back?

01:48:55.125 --> 01:48:57.371
MATT: It's pushed back, yeah, so it's not in
contact with you.

01:48:57.371 --> 01:48:59.707
TALIESIN: Yeah, you got to see if you can get up
