01:48:59.707 --> 01:49:03.010
MARISHA: Yeah, that's cool. I will stand up.

01:49:03.010 --> 01:49:04.499
MATT: Okay.

01:49:04.499 --> 01:49:18.372
MARISHA: Rise up! This guy in front of me is
almost dead, right?

01:49:18.372 --> 01:49:20.494
MATT: He's looking pretty rough, yeah.

01:49:20.494 --> 01:49:23.402
SAM: Focus on the dragon.

01:49:23.402 --> 01:49:25.986
TRAVIS: What was that?

01:49:25.986 --> 01:49:27.392
SAM: "Focus on the dragon."

01:49:27.392 --> 01:49:28.896
TRAVIS: "Focus on the dragon."

01:49:28.896 --> 01:49:32.898
MARISHA: How far away is Thordak from me?

01:49:32.898 --> 01:49:38.965
MATT: Quite a ways away. I'd say close to 65, 70
feet from you.

01:49:38.965 --> 01:49:56.687
MARISHA: Okay. I am going to-- Can I move up one
square closer to Thordak, but not get near the--

01:49:56.687 --> 01:49:58.718
MATT: Yeah, right there, you can.

01:49:58.718 --> 01:50:02.667
MARISHA: But I'm in this cloud, too! Shit.

