01:50:05.007 --> 01:50:10.067
MARISHA: I don't, but that's nice. And now I'm
going to--

01:50:10.067 --> 01:50:12.126
MATT: You are immune to poison, just so you're
aware.

01:50:12.126 --> 01:50:13.192
MARISHA: Am I?

01:50:13.192 --> 01:50:14.612
MATT: Because of the Heroes' Feast.

01:50:14.612 --> 01:50:16.559
MARISHA: Oh, because of the Heroes' Feast! Oh,
