02:36:48.875 --> 02:36:50.688
LIAM: Oh no, it's this die.

02:36:50.688 --> 02:36:53.658
SAM: Oh, you can reduce that by one point, Matt
Mercer.

02:36:53.658 --> 02:36:59.015
MATT: (laughing) Oh no. What did you get? Nah,
