02:36:59.015 --> 02:37:03.475
SAM: My dexterity saving throw. Terrible, 15.

02:37:03.475 --> 02:37:05.553
MATT: Jarett does not make it either.

02:37:05.553 --> 02:37:07.790
LIAM: Big eight, big eight.

02:37:07.790 --> 02:37:09.460
MATT: All right, well.

02:37:09.460 --> 02:37:13.442
LAURA: One of our Jaeger controllers did worse
