02:37:40.848 --> 02:37:42.747
SAM: Where's Pike? What's Pike doing?

02:37:42.747 --> 02:37:48.143
LAURA: Pike is-- Wait, minus 50. She's at 50
minus--she's at 34 points right now.

02:37:48.143 --> 02:37:54.394
TALIESIN: In combat range of a dragon.

02:37:54.394 --> 02:37:59.385
TRAVIS: I never finished my turn, so can I use my
