02:38:19.916 --> 02:38:23.142
TRAVIS: 29?

02:38:23.142 --> 02:38:24.988
MATT: 29 hits.

02:38:24.988 --> 02:38:37.675
TRAVIS: Yeah, not Great Weapon Master. Nine plus
