MATT: Oh yes, you should. Sorry, thank you.

02:38:54.023 --> 02:38:56.087
SAM: I rolled a-- what do I add to it?

02:38:56.087 --> 02:39:00.317
MATT: It's a constitution saving throw, so you add
your constitution save.

02:39:00.317 --> 02:39:03.504
SAM: Constitution? So 18.

02:39:03.504 --> 02:39:10.845
MATT: With that, Bigby's Hand fades, the spell
knocked asunder. Thank you for reminding me of

02:39:10.845 --> 02:39:15.148
that. So that comes to end that turn.

02:39:15.148 --> 02:39:17.398
MARISHA: He has to roll a save.

