02:39:28.534 --> 02:39:33.436
MARISHA: Yeah. He has to roll under a five.

02:39:33.436 --> 02:39:35.702
MATT: Same thing. So with that, the third save is
made, Contagion.

02:39:35.702 --> 02:39:40.562
SAM: At least it won't eat up my Cutting Words any
more.

02:39:40.562 --> 02:39:48.060
MARISHA: It's resting in peace with my 8th-level
spell and her dragon-slaying arrow. They're in a

02:39:48.060 --> 02:39:49.315
puddle somewhere.

02:39:49.315 --> 02:39:50.889
MATT: It's a rough couple rounds.

02:39:50.889 --> 02:39:56.030
LAURA: Did I see where that dragon-slaying arrow
