02:40:28.076 --> 02:40:36.610
you. That's a natural one. Does not hit you. The
stinger, however, is a natural 20. Wow! So that is

02:40:36.610 --> 02:40:44.088
for 12 points of piercing damage to you and I need
you to make a constitution saving throw.

02:40:44.088 --> 02:40:46.119
LIAM and TALIESIN: Poison immunity.

02:40:46.119 --> 02:40:47.876
MATT: That's right. So no effect.

02:40:47.876 --> 02:40:49.106
LAURA: 12 points of damage.

02:40:49.106 --> 02:41:01.687
MATT: The rider is going to swing at you with a
heavy club and then a javelin. That is a 16.

02:41:01.687 --> 02:41:03.495
What's your AC?

02:41:03.495 --> 02:41:04.690
LAURA: 21.

02:41:04.690 --> 02:41:15.886
MATT: Nope. And no. Misses you with both. You're
just too quick for him. The giant sees Percy lying

02:41:15.886 --> 02:41:25.396
on the ground and goes (yells). With its giant
two-handed sword, it's going to make two attacks

02:41:25.396 --> 02:41:33.066
against Percy with advantage. 19, so that's 30 for
the first one.

02:41:33.066 --> 02:41:34.967
TALIESIN: Oh, that just hits.

02:41:34.967 --> 02:41:38.189
MATT: And a 22 with the second.

02:41:38.189 --> 02:41:39.657
TALIESIN: That also just hits.

02:41:39.657 --> 02:41:44.210
MATT: All right. So you take 28 points of slashing
damage from each hit.

02:41:44.210 --> 02:41:48.022
TALIESIN: So that's 28 times two.

02:41:48.022 --> 02:41:49.822
LAURA: 56.

02:41:49.822 --> 02:41:55.250
TALIESIN: 56. All right, that's fine. I blame you
for all of this.

02:41:55.250 --> 02:41:57.195
SAM: We're getting in flute range soon.

02:41:57.195 --> 02:42:03.053
TALIESIN: I'll be hearing about it from the
kitchen. It'll be great. I'll be working on my new

02:42:03.053 --> 02:42:04.482
character.

02:42:04.482 --> 02:42:09.843
MATT: All right. That brings us to--

02:42:09.843 --> 02:42:11.283
SAM: Raishan?

