02:42:51.813 --> 02:42:54.862
LAURA: No way! Oh, I thought you said the face.

02:42:54.862 --> 02:42:57.373
SAM: He has crazy glue on his person?

02:42:57.373 --> 02:43:00.910
MATT: Like any good dungeon master should. So
you're inside this building right now.

02:43:00.910 --> 02:43:11.809
LAURA: If I'm hasted, does that affect my broom?

02:43:11.809 --> 02:43:13.132
MATT: No.

02:43:13.132 --> 02:43:15.320
LAURA: So I just run out.

02:43:15.320 --> 02:43:20.553
MATT: So you just run out this way. You have a lot
of movement speed, so you're still out here at

02:43:20.553 --> 02:43:22.471
half movement.

02:43:22.471 --> 02:43:28.751
LAURA: Okay. Then I'm going to run through the
building and under Raishan and shoot up at Thordak

02:43:28.751 --> 02:43:30.391
from through the building.

02:43:30.391 --> 02:43:33.611
LIAM: Ditch the broom.

02:43:33.611 --> 02:43:36.121
MATT: Go for it. Make your shots.

02:43:36.121 --> 02:43:51.321
LAURA: Okay. Oh no, that one doesn't hit. Okay,
second one. Okay, that hits. That's 29.

02:43:51.321 --> 02:43:53.644
MATT: 29. All right.

02:43:53.644 --> 02:43:56.063
LAURA: Can I do that with a poison arrow? I should
have said that before.

02:43:56.063 --> 02:43:57.567
MATT: You should have said that before.

02:43:57.567 --> 02:44:22.520
LAURA: Never mind. 18, that's with four lightning.
I do get sneak attack right now. 15 more.

02:44:22.520 --> 02:44:29.865
MATT: Okay. That was the first roll. Second
attack?

02:44:29.865 --> 02:44:35.280
LAURA: Yeah. Should I do the second dragon attack? I'm
