02:44:57.681 --> 02:44:59.042
MATT: Okay.

02:44:59.042 --> 02:45:08.672
LAURA: Oh God. Okay. 17 with one lightning.

02:45:08.672 --> 02:45:11.462
MATT: One lightning damage. All right.

02:45:11.462 --> 02:45:23.873
LAURA: So three more. And how many do I add
for the dragon arrow?

02:45:23.873 --> 02:45:25.372
MATT: I'm looking it up right now, actually.

02:45:25.372 --> 02:45:26.672
SAM: Ooh!

02:45:26.672 --> 02:45:28.717
LAURA: I think it's 10d6. I think.

02:45:28.717 --> 02:45:30.191
SAM: Is it really?

