wither and wither.

02:47:15.268 --> 02:47:17.407
SAM: You have another model?

02:47:17.407 --> 02:47:19.092
LAURA: What?!

02:47:19.092 --> 02:47:21.202
SAM: And it's even bigger.

02:47:21.202 --> 02:47:25.656
LAURA: Look at the puny little fuck.

