02:47:36.821 --> 02:47:38.741
SAM: He's so sad.

02:47:38.741 --> 02:47:48.035
MATT: Now there are hanging folds of dragon hide
skin. The form shrunk, but portions still are

02:47:48.035 --> 02:47:49.629
