02:48:38.986 --> 02:48:42.524
SAM: Come on, Pike. For all the marbles.

02:48:42.524 --> 02:48:44.317
LAURA: 17.

02:48:44.317 --> 02:49:02.537
MATT: Nope. Pike takes 20 points of bludgeoning
