MATT: He's going to fly up--

02:49:19.040 --> 02:49:21.816
SAM: Does Pike get an attack of opportunity?

02:49:21.816 --> 02:49:23.032
TRAVIS: I do!

02:49:23.032 --> 02:49:24.259
LAURA: And Pike does!

02:49:24.259 --> 02:49:26.704
MATT: There we go. You both do.

02:49:26.704 --> 02:49:33.874
TRAVIS: Has his AC changed with his different
