02:49:33.874 --> 02:49:40.446
Master. Natural 20.

02:49:40.446 --> 02:49:41.659
MATT: Really?

02:49:41.659 --> 02:49:43.199
TRAVIS: Yeah, on the first roll.

02:49:43.199 --> 02:49:47.285
LAURA: And Pike rolled a 32.

02:49:47.285 --> 02:49:48.823
SAM: Jesus. What is she attacking with?

02:49:48.823 --> 02:49:49.973
LAURA: Her Mace of Disruption.

02:49:49.973 --> 02:49:51.080
SAM: Yes, she is.

02:49:51.080 --> 02:49:52.996
MATT: So go ahead and roll damage for both of
them.

02:49:52.996 --> 02:49:58.921
TRAVIS: I also have brutal critical which at
thirteenth level, you roll two additional damage dice.

02:49:58.921 --> 02:50:00.269
MATT: Yes, you do.

02:50:00.269 --> 02:50:01.755
TALIESIN: Which you then double, don't you?

02:50:01.755 --> 02:50:06.742
MATT: No. You add those two. So roll the damage
first, and then double the dice.

02:50:06.742 --> 02:50:10.627
LAURA: And then she gets Divine Strike, right? On
her attack.

02:50:10.627 --> 02:50:11.730
MATT: Correct.

02:50:11.730 --> 02:50:14.662
TRAVIS: 28. So I double that?

02:50:14.662 --> 02:50:22.846
MATT: You double the dice. Including the d4 and d6
