02:50:40.276 --> 02:50:41.945
MATT: Nice, and Pike's?

02:50:41.945 --> 02:50:54.378
LAURA: Pike rolled-- fuck. 18. 19! It was 19.

02:50:54.378 --> 02:51:03.794
MATT: Okay. Perfect. You both strike, as the
now-diminished form of Thordak begins to pull

02:51:03.794 --> 02:51:08.965
backward, eyes looking around. The piercing
star-like white light of the eyes seems to have

02:51:08.965 --> 02:51:16.256
