02:51:16.256 --> 02:51:23.681
chest, there is just a gaping hole where bits
of flesh and dragon muscle are hanging out,

02:51:23.681 --> 02:51:30.012
occasionally slopping out of the wound. He's
pulling back. All right.

02:51:30.012 --> 02:51:31.256
LIAM: I'm up.

02:51:31.256 --> 02:51:32.455
MATT: Yep.

02:51:32.455 --> 02:51:38.128
LIAM: I'm going to arc up and land on his head.
