MATT: Misses.

02:51:51.841 --> 02:51:54.175
LIAM: Second attack hits. That's 24.

02:51:54.175 --> 02:51:55.180
MATT: Hits.

02:51:55.180 --> 02:51:58.449
LIAM: Third attack with the dragon sword is a 22.

02:51:58.449 --> 02:52:00.004
MATT: 22 hits.

02:52:00.004 --> 02:52:49.442
LIAM: So, with Whisper. (counting) That's 45 with
