02:53:09.688 --> 02:53:11.374
LAURA and TRAVIS: 45.

02:53:11.374 --> 02:53:14.744
LIAM: So 21 plus 45 is-- So 66.

02:53:14.744 --> 02:53:21.182
LAURA: It's 45 for the first attack, 21
