02:53:36.043 --> 02:53:41.221
MATT: Cool, so that ends Vax's turn. Kima--

02:53:41.221 --> 02:53:46.672
SAM: Oh yeah, the wyvern.

02:53:46.672 --> 02:53:51.333
MATT: That wyvern just can't seem to keep itself
standing.

02:53:51.333 --> 02:54:01.197
SAM: That was really good handwork, I didn't catch
