04:17:07.959 --> 04:17:12.525
TRAVIS: Is that a spell? What level is that?

04:17:12.525 --> 04:17:14.048
ALL: 9th-level.

04:17:14.048 --> 04:17:18.697
LIAM: She just blew her wad, she's done, we got a
dragon and a flute.

04:17:18.697 --> 04:17:20.134
LAURA: She's not done.

04:17:20.134 --> 04:17:26.182
MATT: You're right. She has nothing else up her
sleeve. So. On that note.

04:17:26.182 --> 04:17:27.884
SAM: Matt Mercer.

04:17:27.884 --> 04:17:33.716
MATT: This could possibly be a whole different
encounter, I don't want to keep you guys here

04:17:33.716 --> 04:17:36.727
