04:17:51.095 --> 04:17:54.001
MATT: Yeah, it's going to take a few rounds for
the rest of the party to get here.

04:17:54.001 --> 04:17:55.594
TRAVIS: She didn't get to ask any of the
questions?

04:17:55.594 --> 04:17:58.511
LAURA: She might not have even needed to ask
