04:18:01.539 --> 04:18:03.504
MARISHA: Yeah, maybe she was doing it
telepathically.

04:18:03.504 --> 04:18:05.452
SAM: What are you talking about? She read a
scroll!

04:18:05.452 --> 04:18:09.199
LAURA: Maybe it was just taking his soul into
