04:18:09.199 --> 04:18:10.872
SAM: Information!

04:18:10.872 --> 04:18:17.546
MATT: Regardless. (laugh) We are out for the
evening, thank you all for sticking with us for

04:18:17.546 --> 04:18:19.256
this longer episode.

04:18:19.256 --> 04:18:24.096
LIAM: We should have just let her do what she
